{"title":"山村教师（二首）","authors":["何理"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":9,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村教师（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月色下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在朦胧的月色下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你赤着脚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哗啦哗啦地趟着溪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搭着一块块踏石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏石是你躬身俯卧的化身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子的小脚丫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叭哒叭哒踏过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象踩着你的脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你又背起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得过小儿麻痹的女孩儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沐浴着晨光跨过小溪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口中还轻轻地哼唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了让孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘取未来科学的明珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你甘为人梯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和桥梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小窗口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是一洞天宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隐藏着多少奥妙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深夜最富于魅力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"园丁的心是它的恒星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔下留有漫长的轨迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧的是蜡烛般的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欣慰的是颗颗新星的孕育"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}